strings:
<se_high>*: I don't want to be made into a maid stew!
I don't want to die here!
<se_high>*: I can't die before I've seen my beloved son, Lorenzo, again!
<se_low>*: You have to help us! We'll be a troll's dinner at this rate! Can't you overpower them?

<se_low>*: Fee! Fie! Foe! Yum! ♪
Juicy humans in my tum! ♪
The boss troll is so engrossed in his cooking that he doesn't notice he has company.
